column5: I am trying too find the name of the hydrographic map vendor that's at the show every year.I just went through the vendor list on the shows  website and could not find anything. I need a hydrogaphic map of Nosbonsing lake and if the map vendor is not there this year there's not much point of me going. I hope I missed them under the vendors list. Thanks Rob

Rob if no one gives you this, I have his card somewhere at home from last years show.  I think it was something like FS or something. If not just go to the Canadian Hydrographic Services site and you can order it there. You will just have to do some searching as the site is not user friendly.  I will check when I am home tonight to see if i can find the card.  Mike

Hi Alumacraft, The following are some links that were provided to me by the wonderful folks on this site! Maybe they will help in your search. Jim http://www.adventurefishingmaps.on.ca/ http://www.fishingmapsplus.com/ http://www.trakmaps.com/

Hey Rob,  I cant find that card. I dont know where I put it. If I come across it I will PM you. Sorry.  If not, he should be in that same spot as he has been in the past 2 years.  If I could only remember.....  Mike
Try here        Canadian Hydrographic Service  www.charts.gc.ca  phone 1-877-CHS-LINK
Thanks for the info and links guys I'll check those out.
